INSERT INTO `jobs` VALUES (1,21,'Create a Marketing Campaign for a New Product Launch','We need a marketing specialist to create a marketing campaign for our new product launch. The campaign should include a strategy for social media, email marketing, and advertising. The specialist should have experience in creating successful marketing campaigns and should be able to provide us with samples of their work. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-06 21:09:37','2023-12-02 01:02:09',450000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2,22,'Develop a Chatbot for a Customer Service Platform','We need a chatbot developed for our customer service platform. The chatbot should be able to handle basic customer inquiries and provide helpful responses. It should be integrated with our customer service software and should be able to learn from previous interactions. The chatbot should be developed using Python and should be hosted on AWS. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-24 05:10:43','2023-11-20 14:19:41',5000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3,23,'Develop a Responsive Website for a Travel Agency','We need a responsive website for our travel agency. The website should be mobile-friendly and should have a clean and modern design. It should include a booking system and payment gateway integration. The website should be developed using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and PHP. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-13 10:33:30','2023-12-03 16:43:29',300000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4,24,'Write a Script for Explainer Videos','We are looking for a scriptwriter to write scripts for our explainer videos. The scripts should be engaging and informative and should be suitable for a wide audience. The writer should have experience in writing scripts for videos and should be able to provide us with samples of their work. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-28 20:44:53','2023-10-29 01:17:15',525000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(5,25,'Design a Logo for a New Restaurant','We need a professional logo for our new restaurant. The logo should be modern and reflect the theme of our restaurant. It should include the name of the restaurant and a symbol that represents the theme. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-11 20:19:27','2023-11-09 18:35:21',100000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(6,26,'Write SEO Optimized Articles for a Tech Blog','We are looking for a content writer to write SEO optimized articles for our tech blog. The articles should be informative and engaging for our readers. The writer should have experience in writing for tech blogs and should be able to provide us with samples of their work. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-12 03:42:58','2023-10-19 17:27:58',150000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(7,27,'Develop an E-commerce Website for a Fashion Brand','We need an e-commerce website for our fashion brand. The website should have a clean and modern design and should be mobile-friendly. It should include a shopping cart and payment gateway integration. The website should be developed using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and PHP. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-19 15:42:46','2023-12-22 00:37:33',2000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,28,'Design a Mobile App for a Fitness Tracker','We need a mobile app designed for our fitness tracker. The app should be user-friendly and should include features such as step tracking, calorie tracking, and workout tracking. The app should be designed for both iOS and Android platforms. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-13 18:22:12','2023-12-16 01:53:50',500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,29,'Write a Business Plan for a Start-up Company','We are looking for a business plan writer to write a detailed business plan for our start-up company. The plan should include a market analysis, financial projections, and a marketing strategy. The writer should have experience in writing business plans and should be able to provide us with samples of their work. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-09 12:55:47','2023-10-17 06:45:05',215000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(10,30,'Develop a Mobile Game for iOS and Android','We need a mobile game developed for both iOS and Android platforms. The game should be user-friendly and should be suitable for all ages. It should include features such as in-app purchases and social media integration. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-21 22:21:18','2023-10-27 08:55:58',3000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(11,31,'Develop a Custom WordPress Plugin','We need a WordPress developer to create a custom plugin for our website. The plugin should be able to add custom functionality to our website and should be easy to use. It should be developed using PHP and should be compatible with the latest version of WordPress. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-22 02:37:36','2024-01-01 05:16:37',25000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(12,32,'Design a User Interface for a Financial Management Application','We need a user interface designer to create a modern and intuitive interface for our financial management application. The interface should be designed for desktop and mobile devices and should be easy to navigate. It should include features such as account summary, transaction history, and budget tracking. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-02 23:26:56','2023-10-19 10:37:23',270000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(13,33,'Edit and Proofread a 100-page Novel','We are looking for an experienced editor to edit and proofread a 100-page novel. The editor should have a strong background in literature and be able to provide feedback on the story structure, character development, and overall writing style. The editor should also be proficient in grammar, syntax, and spelling. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-11 17:47:16','2023-11-09 18:38:23',800000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(14,34,'Create a Brand Identity for a New Coffee Shop','We are looking for a graphic designer to create a brand identity for our new coffee shop. The designer should be able to create a logo, packaging design, and other marketing materials that reflect our brand values and target audience. The designer should also be proficient in using Adobe Creative Suite. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-16 21:07:19','2023-11-06 14:48:11',1500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(15,35,'Translate a 50-page Legal Document from English to Arabic','We need a professional translator to translate a 50-page legal document from English to Arabic. The translator should have a strong background in legal terminology and be able to provide accurate translations that preserve the original meaning of the document. The translator should also be proficient in using CAT tools. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-06-03 20:25:44','2023-10-05 18:22:26',400000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(16,36,'Develop a Mobile App for a Fitness Coach','We need a mobile app developed for a fitness coach. The app should include features such as workout plans, progress tracking, and nutrition advice. The app should be developed for both iOS and Android platforms and should be user-friendly and responsive. The app should be developed using Flutter. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-09 18:07:22','2023-12-27 09:28:06',2500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(17,37,'Create a Social Media Marketing Strategy for a Beauty Brand','We need a social media marketer to create a marketing strategy for our beauty brand. The marketer should have experience in creating successful social media campaigns and be able to identify the target audience and create engaging content that resonates with them. The marketer should also be proficient in using social media analytics tools. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-03-12 12:19:38','2023-12-31 06:15:43',1200000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(18,38,'Create a 3D Model of a Building for an Architectural Visualization Project','We need a 3D artist to create a realistic 3D model of a building for an architectural visualization project. The model should include accurate details and textures and should be suitable for rendering in different lighting conditions. The artist should be proficient in using 3D modeling software such as SketchUp, 3ds Max, or Blender. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-21 18:19:57','2023-12-22 08:26:13',500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(19,39,'Develop a Machine Learning Algorithm for Predictive Maintenance','We need a data scientist to develop a machine learning algorithm for predictive maintenance of industrial equipment. The algorithm should be able to predict equipment failures based on historical data and provide recommendations for maintenance actions. The data scientist should be proficient in using Python and machine learning libraries such as Scikit-learn or TensorFlow. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-05-03 17:30:25','2023-10-22 15:13:39',3000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(20,40,'Create an Animated Explainer Video for a Healthcare Startup','We need an animator to create an animated explainer video for our healthcare startup. The video should be engaging and informative and should explain our product and its benefits to potential customers. The animator should be proficient in using animation software such as After Effects or Adobe Animate. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-12 00:42:44','2023-10-03 12:20:00',1000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(21,41,'Design a User Interface for a Mobile Game','We need a UI/UX designer to design a user interface for our mobile game. The designer should be able to create visually appealing and intuitive interfaces that enhance the user experience. The designer should also be proficient in using design tools such as Sketch or Adobe XD. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-24 14:09:30','2023-10-05 10:40:50',700000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(22,42,'Write a Business Plan for a Social Media Marketing Agency','We are looking for a business plan writer to write a comprehensive business plan for our social media marketing agency. The plan should include a market analysis, a marketing strategy, financial projections, and an operational plan. The writer should be proficient in business writing and have experience in writing business plans. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project.','2023-04-20 00:05:24','2023-11-30 16:39:32',800000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(23,43,'Write SEO-Optimized Articles for a Travel Blog','We are a travel company looking for a talented writer to create SEO-optimized articles for our travel blog. The articles should be informative, engaging, and tailored towards our target audience. You will be responsible for conducting research on different travel destinations and creating content that is both interesting and useful. The ideal candidate should have excellent writing skills, be familiar with SEO techniques, and have a passion for travel. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. Each article should be at least 1000 words long. We are looking to hire for a long-term basis, so please apply only if you are interested in ongoing work.','2023-03-14 08:22:16','2023-12-09 20:36:34',500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(24,44,'Design a Logo and Brand Identity for a New E-commerce Store','We are launching a new e-commerce store and we need a talented designer to create a logo and brand identity for us. The logo should be simple, memorable, and reflect the nature of our business. You will also be responsible for creating a brand identity that is consistent with our logo and reflects our brand values. The ideal candidate should have experience in branding and logo design, be creative, and have a good eye for detail. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. We are looking to hire for a one-time project, but there may be additional design work available in the future.','2023-03-12 09:10:25','2023-10-09 05:22:16',700000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(25,45,'Develop a Mobile App for Mental Health Management','We are a healthcare company looking for a skilled app developer to create a mobile app for mental health management. The app should allow users to track their mood, set goals, and receive personalized recommendations for self-care based on their data. Users should also be able to connect with mental health professionals and access resources and articles on mental health. The ideal candidate should have experience in mobile app development, be proficient in iOS and Android development, and have a good understanding of mental health. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. We are looking to hire for a long-term basis, so there may be additional development work available in the future.','2023-03-10 06:22:15','2023-12-09 16:26:14',2000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(26,46,'Develop a Cross-Platform Mobile App for a Fitness Company','We are a fitness company looking for an experienced Flutter developer to create a cross-platform mobile app for our business. The app should allow users to view and book classes, track their progress, and access nutrition information. The ideal candidate should have experience in mobile app development using Flutter, be proficient in Dart programming language, and have a good understanding of UI/UX design principles. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. We are looking to hire for a long-term basis, so there may be additional development work available in the future.','2023-04-29 12:46:13','2023-11-10 10:51:44',1500000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(27,47,'Create a Social Media Mobile App for a Startup','We are a startup looking for a skilled Flutter developer to create a social media mobile app for our business. The app should allow users to create profiles, post content, and interact with other users. The ideal candidate should have experience in mobile app development using Flutter, be proficient in Dart programming language, and have a good understanding of social media app development. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. We are looking to hire for a long-term basis, so there may be additional development work available in the future.','2023-03-07 22:09:38','2023-11-27 21:25:03',2000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(28,48,'Develop a Mobile App for a Real Estate Company','We are a real estate company looking for a talented Flutter developer to create a mobile app for our business. The app should allow users to search for properties, view property details, and contact agents. The ideal candidate should have experience in mobile app development using Flutter, be proficient in Dart programming language, and have a good understanding of UI/UX design principles. Please provide us with your portfolio and estimated timeline for the project. We are looking to hire for a long-term basis, so there may be additional development work available in the future.','2023-05-31 15:08:21','2023-11-16 22:25:27',1000000,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(29,49,'Build a Web Application Using Django Framework','We are looking for a skilled developer to build a web application using the Django framework. The application